파일은 있어도 파일을 읽을수 없는 상태
접근자체가 불가능



chcon -t

restorecon 

[root@servera ~]# ls -Z
unconfined_u:object_r:admin_home_t:s0 file1
[root@servera ~]# chcon -t httpd_sys_content_t  file1
[root@servera ~]# restorecon -Rv /root 
Relabeled /root/file1 from unconfined_u:object_r:httpd_sys_content_t:s0 to unconfined_u:object_r:admin_home_t:s0



